  <div id="text-content_3c7f3610-75ab-4cbe-823c-3834fcdb862b" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can reply to any discussion or discussion reply in the Discussions Redesign interface.</p>
<p>If the steps in this lesson do not match what is displayed in your course, learn how to <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-reply-to-a-discussion-as-an-instructor/ta-p/1110" target="_blank">reply to a discussion in the classic Discussions interface.</a></p>
<p><strong>Notes:</strong> </p>
<ul>
<li>If the <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-create-a-discussion-using-Discussions-Redesign-as-an/ta-p/504145" target="_blank">anonymous discussion option is enabled for the discussion</a>, student names and profile pictures do not display. However, as an instructor, your name and profile picture is visible to all course members.</li>
<li>If there are no discussion submissions, you can edit the anonymity details.</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussions" data-step-uuid="efa1809c-f4c1-4e22-b10a-b69c25b04b7f">
    <h2 id="open_discussions" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Discussions</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/433/231/original/1a0ee09e-7821-4fe3-be5a-82f8400ae626.png" srcset="" alt="Open Discussions" height="258" width="175">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_a87ff749-3493-4f05-8346-cd6fe0b49023" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Discussions</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_discussion_topic" data-step-uuid="845748b8-22f9-400c-b590-a4284704526f">
    <h2 id="open_discussion_topic" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Discussion</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/433/233/original/6dcf036d-8845-4c45-9da2-336a2c4cf2c9.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/433/233/medium/6dcf036d-8845-4c45-9da2-336a2c4cf2c9.png" srcset="" alt="Open Discussion" height="170" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_86a86fc0-3c13-47c8-8f87-350c086e963a" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the name of the discussion.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="reply_to_discussion_topic" data-step-uuid="6652d09b-eac2-4c97-9b8a-a1b68831484a">
    <h2 id="reply_to_discussion_topic" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Reply to Discussion</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/648/960/original/213bcf8a-05c0-4b6c-8fee-c750ae5113e2.png" srcset="" alt="Reply to Discussion" height="494" width="837">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_63c9bf99-2838-4435-8979-ef18e706cfd2" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To reply to the main discussion, click the <strong>Reply</strong> button. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="post_a_message" data-step-uuid="58c84ef5-0ba3-434d-9425-06afd26d86a1">
    <h3 id="post_a_message" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Post Reply</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/433/238/original/41b53e45-d99f-4636-8d39-058f568c980f.png" srcset="" alt="Post Reply" height="365" width="799">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_f6d913c5-4b68-4872-af5c-8c1e5113f833" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To enter your reply, add links, photos, equations, and/or media, use the Rich Content Editor [1]. </p>
<p>To post your reply, click the<strong> Reply</strong> button [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view_your_reply" data-step-uuid="9e023da3-7a36-4561-aff1-0f33a087d4c7">
    <h3 id="view_your_reply" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Your Reply</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/648/962/original/17f7cdf2-0db7-4e5c-8e55-ca6bbd43864e.png" srcset="" alt="View Your Reply" height="250" width="599">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_cb5730cd-bb8c-4af9-9270-608fd391906e" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Your reply displays at the top of the discussion replies.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="reply_to_a_comment_in_a_focused_discussion" data-step-uuid="077dfe7b-5f06-4e07-8e71-6ac68c0eb719">
    <h2 id="reply_to_a_comment_in_a_focused_discussion" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Thread a Discussion Reply</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/648/964/original/7cd25a01-19f2-4f2a-9dc7-91862598c9d7.png" srcset="" alt="Thread a Discussion Reply" height="331" width="657">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_5e136013-1e6c-4d99-9532-18158fbabb41" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To respond to a discussion reply, click the <strong>Reply</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="post-a-message" data-step-uuid="c74b46d3-c5c8-4d77-bf90-4edadbab2ea9">
    <h3 id="post-a-message" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Post Threaded Reply</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/733/319/original/54728838-e2a1-41bd-ba2a-aa4e92cbaa58.png" srcset="" alt="Post Threaded Reply" height="702" width="780">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_cccde8f9-b5c7-4269-bcfa-e08bfd9ac620" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the discussion thread replies sidebar, add your reply, links, files, and other media in the Rich Content Editor [1].</p>
<p>To post your reply, click the<strong> Reply</strong> button [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
